docs.lead_paragraph: BERN, Switzerland, Aug. 21 (AP) -- The United States Olympic track team, winding up competitive training for the Rome games, dominated an international meet today. Even though taking it easy, the Americans equaled one world record and served notice of peak fitness for the 1960 test.
